[normal]STEM subjects in Girlguid
[normal]i
[normal]ng’s youth programmes
[normal]&#xa0;[bold]Girlguiding’s programme for girls and young 
[normal]women includes activities and resources that challenge the gender stereotypes that our evidence shows influence girls
[normal]’
[normal] decisions about subject choice and career aspirations. 
[normal]It also includes specific focus on STEM subjects. 
